#### Abstract:

In today's fast-paced world, managing shared expenses among friends, family, or colleagues can be a cumbersome and error-prone task. 
The Expense Sharing app is designed to simplify and streamline the process of tracking and splitting expenses, making financial management a breeze for users. 
This abstract provides an overview of the key features and benefits of the Expense Sharing app.
The Expense Sharing app offers a user-friendly interface accessible on both mobile and web platforms. 
Users can effortlessly create groups and invite members to join, allowing for easy collaboration on shared expenses. 
Within each group, users can record expenses incurred by individuals and upload receipts for added transparency.
